author: lryan
msg: Fix for dangerous DOM cloning behavior in template processing. Cloning nodes from a singleton template DOM across many gadget renders can cause those cloned nodes to accumulate in the singleton''s template Document userData. Use importNode across different documents and cloning within the same document to avoid issue.
